languages.text: "Судя по голосам — много. Злые. Зубастые, но не слишком. Берут толпой..."
"Judging by the voices, there's a lot of them. Angry. They've got teeth, but they aren't that sharp. Their strength is their numbers..."

languages.text: 「声を聞くかぎり、大勢のものが向かっていて…怒っているみたい。敵意はあるものの攻撃力はさほどない。彼らの強みは数の多さでしょう…」
languages.original_text: "Judging by the voices, there's a lot of them. Angry. They've got teeth, but they aren't that sharp. Their strength is their numbers..."

traits.locale_text: 「声を聞くかぎり、大勢のものが向かっていて…怒っているみたい。敵意はあるものの攻撃力はさほどない。彼らの強みは数の多さでしょう…」

languages.text: “从声音判断，他们有很多人，都很生气。他们长着尖牙，却又没有那么锋利。他们的优势在于人数众多……”
languages.original_text: "Judging by the voices, there's a lot of them. Angry. They've got teeth, but they aren't that sharp. Their strength is their numbers..."

traits.locale_text: “从声音判断，他们有很多人，都很生气。他们长着尖牙，却又没有那么锋利。他们的优势在于人数众多……”

languages.text: «A juzgar por las voces, son bastantes. Y están enfadados. Dientes tienen, pero no muy afilados. Su fuerza radica en el número...».
languages.original_text: "Judging by the voices, there's a lot of them. Angry. They've got teeth, but they aren't that sharp. Their strength is their numbers..."

traits.locale_text: «A juzgar por las voces, son bastantes. Y están enfadados. Dientes tienen, pero no muy afilados. Su fuerza radica en el número...».

languages.text: « À en juger par les voix, ils sont nombreux et en colère. Ils ont des crocs, mais pas vraiment aiguisés. Leur force tient dans la taille de leur groupe... »

languages.text: "Den Stimmen nach zu schließen, sind es viele. Wütend. Sie haben Zähne, aber die sind nicht sehr spitz. Ihre Stärke ist ihre Anzahl ..."

languages.text: "Seslere bakılırsa kalabalıklar. Öfkeliler. Dişleri var ama çok da keskin değil. Asıl güçlerini sayıca üstünlüklerinden alıyorlar."

traits.locale_text: "Seslere bakılacak olursa çok fazlalar. Öfkeliler. Dişleri var ama fazla keskin değil. Asıl güçlerini sayıca kalabalık olmalarından alıyorlar."
